{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slum Dweller is an immersive, physically simulated fighting game that offers players a unique experience of becoming an ordinary slum dweller, trying to survive in harsh criminal environment or a street fighter, fighting underground brutal tournaments ongoing in modern slums. With its innovative combat system, players can use their mouse or joystick to easily control their characters, allowing them to feel the intensity and thrill of each battle as they face off against formidable opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/ragdoll12s.gif?t=1734570547\" /><strong>Physically Based Combat</strong>: prepare for an unparalleled combat experience where your every move matters. All animations and maneuvers are meticulously designed with a strong foundation in realism. Each character has its own unique set of attributes, including weight, strength, endurance, and agility, which affect their ability to move, deal damage and take a hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/parking_for_gif_7s.gif?t=1734570547\" /><strong>Local PvP:</strong> challenge your friends with shared screen as in good old times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sandbox mode: </strong>build your own levels and challenges to express your creativity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Variety of characters and levels: </strong>take part in one-vs-one, one-vs-many or crowd-vs-crowd fights to prove your dominance among slum dwellers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1734570547\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734570547","backgroun